{"tid":898401,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［犯罪學］其實強姦罪和非禮罪犯人","createTime":"2018-11-11T16:03:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T13:06:25.000Z","uid":149978,"like":25,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ef3a7c6d3099d97cf60227bdf2753dbaea20aa67","tid":898401,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:03:54.000Z","msg":"非禮強姦都係性衝動引起。<br />\n在心理學及預防犯罪角度看，<br />\n強姦犯犯人，判佢地必須接受強制睪丸切除手術 + 服用抗雄激素 + 賠錢俾受害人。<br />\n非禮罪就判佢地，強制服用抗雄激素及心理治療。<br />\n<br />\n係咪比監禁合理 ？<br />\n又可以完全杜絕重犯的可能。<br />\n<br />\n如果強姦有暴力成份，<br />\n就分開兩件案處理。<br />\n暴力要坐監，強姦要切睪丸。"},{"pid":"41d42b82c59e416180c55f7afeab2492c53ab485","tid":898401,"uid":30836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:05:43.000Z","msg":"監禁嘅目的係乜？<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🤔</span>"},{"pid":"fcb6d4b88ef94009e0ee3f091f8c04b5009f18b4","tid":898401,"uid":41138,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:07:43.000Z","msg":"放心，人在做天地看。"},{"pid":"e52f6c3c36946d28cfb8157f5ff3ae21fa5de17a","tid":898401,"uid":69779,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:10:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7442e3200daa89b3c8635bbc446b934c11712c","tid":898401,"uid":69779,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:10:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4ef338a09d1a323b67562669c92f6d18a9543489","tid":898401,"uid":12252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac7442e3200daa89b3c8635bbc446b934c11712c","tid":898401,"uid":69779,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:10:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:36:49.000Z","msg":"睪丸切除都唔夠懲罰同阻嚇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw冇